From: Robby Cai <r63905@freescale.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Feb 2015 19:39:04 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] MLK-10278-5 Enable EPDC and PXP on i.MX7d

Enable PXP and EPDC for EPDC to work

Signed-off-by: Robby Cai <r63905@freescale.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig
index 3644010..002ac32 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx_v7_defconfig
@@ -251,6 +251,7 @@ CONFIG_FB_MXC_MIPI_DSI=y
 CONFIG_FB_MXC_TRULY_WVGA_SYNC_PANEL=y
 CONFIG_FB_MXC_HDMI=y
 CONFIG_FB_MXC_EINK_PANEL=y
+CONFIG_FB_MXC_EINK_V2_PANEL=y
 CONFIG_FB_MXS_SII902X=y
 CONFIG_FB_MXC_DCIC=m
 CONFIG_HANNSTAR_CABC=y
@@ -332,6 +333,7 @@ CONFIG_RTC_DRV_MXC=y
 CONFIG_RTC_DRV_SNVS=y
 CONFIG_DMADEVICES=y
 CONFIG_MXC_PXP_V2=y
+CONFIG_MXC_PXP_V3=y
 CONFIG_IMX_SDMA=y
 CONFIG_MXS_DMA=y
 CONFIG_STAGING=y
